The paper is about forecasting the impact of transformative AI technologies on society, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The survey also includes questions about the impact of computational resources on AI research, which could be classified under Cybersecurity and Privacy (cs.CY). Additionally, the survey includes questions about the potential impact on human tasks and society, which could be classified under Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The survey also includes questions about forecasting and uncertainty, which could be classified under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
